@startuml

left to right direction

actor GameDeveloper as Dev
actor Player as Player
actor "Arcade Library" as Arcade
actor "Resource Store\n(JSON, images)" as Resources

rectangle "GraphicNovel Framework" as System {
  usecase "Create GraphicNovel view\n(GraphicNovel())" as UC_Create
  usecase "Configure characters\n(.characters setter)" as UC_Chars
  usecase "Register events\n(add_event)" as UC_Events
  usecase "Load dialog from JSON\n(setup -> parser_dialog.parsing)" as UC_Load
  usecase "Remap input keys\n(input_handler.change_key)" as UC_Keymap
  usecase "Start and show view\n(window.show_view)" as UC_Show
  usecase "Advance dialog\n(ENTER or mapped key -> next_dlg_command)" as UC_Next
  usecase "Toggle skipping\n(TAB or mapped key -> skip_dlg_command)" as UC_Skip
  usecase "Hide/Show GUI\n(H or mapped key -> hide_gui_command)" as UC_Hide
  usecase "Pick menu choice\n(UIFlatButton click)" as UC_Menu
  usecase "Submit text/int input\n(UIInputText + event)" as UC_Input
  usecase "Render & update\n(on_draw, update)" as UC_Render
  usecase "Load textures/backgrounds\n(load_texture, resources)" as UC_Tex
  usecase "End-of-dialog callback\n(on_ended)" as UC_End
}

Dev --> UC_Create
Dev --> UC_Chars
Dev --> UC_Events
Dev --> UC_Load
Dev --> UC_Keymap
Dev --> UC_Show
Dev --> UC_End

Player --> UC_Next
Player --> UC_Skip
Player --> UC_Hide
Player --> UC_Menu
Player --> UC_Input

Arcade --> UC_Render
Arcade --> UC_Tex

Resources --> UC_Load
Resources --> UC_Tex

UC_Render .> UC_Show : depends on
UC_Load .> UC_Tex : uses

@enduml